    ============================================================
    Telegram Trade Manager
    LocalScript / Executor Script
    ============================================================
    Allows remote trade management via a Telegram bot.
    Supports up to 4 configuration profiles, each keyed by
    Telegram User ID AND Roblox User ID.

    Uses executor's HTTP request function to bypass Roblox's
    api.telegram.org block.
    ============================================================
--]]

